## What this file does not cover

- Setup (init.sh, bootstrap.sh — run once).
- Internal checker structure (read `.now/src/` when a failure
  needs diagnosis).
- The hook chain (read `.now/hooks/` if the enforcement sequence
  itself is in question).
- Git plumbing (abstracted by the act layer).

If I am reaching for any of the above during normal work, I have
dropped out of the stance. Return to the acts.

